":"Gn 22:14","book":"Gen","chapter":22,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the lamb for the burnt offering, my son.” Then the two of them walked on together."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 22:14","book":"Gen","chapter":22,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit see"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:22:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When they arrived at the place that God had told him about, Abraham built the altar there and arranged the wood. He bound his son Isaac "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or Isaac hand and foot"},{"kind":"text","text":" and placed him on the altar "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:17","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:21","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" on top of the wood. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 11:17","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":17},{"label":"Jms 2:21","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or Isaac hand and foot"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:22:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then Abraham reached out and took the knife to slaughter his son."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:22:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the angel of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" called to him from heaven and said, “Abraham, Abraham!”"},{"kind":"text","text":" He replied, “Here I am.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:22:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then he said, “Do not lay a hand on the boy or do anything to him. For now I know that you fear God, since you have not withheld your only son from me.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:32","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:32","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:22:13","